  "title": "Resident Aesthetic Doctor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Lazz Aesthetic is a professional Aesthetic Medical Clinic. Our client is from mid to high end. Our commitment is to deliver scientifically proven evidence-based aesthetic and age management treatments with genuine care. Our employees are passionately committed to fundamentally change the future of medical aesthetic and age management care.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform medical-grade aesthetic treatments including injectables (Botox, skin boosters, fillers), Pico Laser, Helio laser treatments, chemical peels, and thread lifts to achieve optimal patient outcomes</li><li>Develop and implement personalized patient treatment plans by assessing patient concerns and recommending appropriate aesthetic procedures</li><li>Conduct thorough consultations to educate patients on treatment options, expected results, and care protocols</li><li>Monitor and review patient progress regularly to adjust treatment plans and ensure high standards of care</li><li>Manage patient enquiries effectively, providing clear and accurate information about treatment courses and post-treatment care</li><li>Train and mentor clinical staff to uphold clinical excellence and consistent patient care standards</li><li>Foster a collaborative and respectful workplace environment that supports team performance and patient satisfaction</li><li>Promote a friendly, warm, and exceptional patient experience throughout all interactions</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Medical degree: MBBS, MBChB, MBBCh, MD or equivalent</li><li>Registration with the Singapore Medical Council</li><li>Attainment of all relevant Certificate of Competence (COCs) for aesthetic procedures</li></ul>",
